  = headline_with_flash 'Browsing headings'

  markdown:
    - Use `H` and `Shift + H` to jump to the next / previous heading
    - Use `1` and `Shift + 1` to jump to the next / previous heading 1 (you can do that up to heading 6 with the respective number key)
    - Use `Insert + F7`, followed by `Option + H`, to open the headings outline

    [CSS counters](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/CSS/Counters) are used to generate the hierarchical heading numbers (superscripted at the end of each heading).

